---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="刘扬 - 产品经理 / 独立创作者">
  <main class="home">
    <article class="paper">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="masthead">
        <div class="masthead-inner">
          <span class="masthead-label">Portfolio</span>
          <h1 class="masthead-title">刘扬</h1>
          <p class="masthead-subtitle">产品经理 · 独立开发者 · 内容创作者</p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="section">
        <div class="intro-block">
          <div class="avatar-column">
            <div class="avatar">
              <img src="/肖像照横屏.png" alt="刘扬" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bio-column">
            <p class="bio-text">
              汕头大学网络与新媒体专业，GPA 4.01/5，专业排名第一。
              热衷于用产品思维解决实际问题，正在探索 AI 与学习的交汇点。
            </p>
            <p class="bio-text">
              我是一名对产品充满热情的学生，喜欢从用户视角出发，发现问题并尝试解决。
              在校期间，我独立完成了 <a href="https://wisdio.org" target="_blank" class="link">Wisdio</a> 这款 AI 学习工具的从0到1，
              涵盖用户调研、产品设计、原型开发和部署上线。
            </p>
            <p class="bio-text">
              此前，我在北京日报社实习，发表了23篇报道，其中3篇登上头版。
              这段经历锻炼了我的信息收集与表达能力，也让我更懂得如何讲好一个故事。
            </p>
            <div class="contact-info">
              <span class="contact-item">leoyoung_work@outlook.com</span>
              <span class="contact-divider">·</span>
              <span class="contact-item">微信: LeoYoung_H</span>
              <span class="contact-divider">·</span>
              <a href="https://xhslink.com/m/9ji8tv9wtWA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">小红书</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Projects -->
      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">项目作品</h2>
        
        <div class="project-item featured">
          <div class="project-header">
            <span class="project-name">Wisdio</span>
            <span class="project-tag">独立产品</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">
            基于 LLM 的视频学习浏览器插件，支持 AI 对话、智能总结、自定义 Prompt。
            针对 Bilibili/YouTube 长视频学习中"视觉信息过载、被动接受且难以沉淀知识"的痛点，
            设计端到端视频对话交互体验。
          </p>
          <a href="https://wisdio.org" target="_blank" class="project-link">wisdio.org →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="project-item">
          <div class="project-header">
            <span class="project-name">Grammar Check</span>
            <span class="project-tag">产品设计</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">
            AI 智能写作校对编辑器。首创"上下文聚焦定位"功能，设计分片并发校对策略，
            目标AI输出成功率 > 99.5%，确保作者对文本的完整掌控权。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="project-item">
          <div class="project-header">
            <span class="project-name">Cure</span>
            <span class="project-tag">毕业设计</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">
            中风患者居家康复可穿戴设备与严肃游戏。结合 CV、EMG 技术与游戏化策略，
            旨在提升中风患者居家康复锻炼的依从性。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Works Preview -->
      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">近期作品</h2>
        
        <div class="works-grid">
          <a href="/showcase/articles" class="work-card">
            <span class="work-category">数据分析</span>
            <h3 class="work-title">AI新闻区分度研究</h3>
            <p class="work-desc">问卷调查 · 795份样本回归分析</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/showcase/articles" class="work-card">
            <span class="work-category">视频类</span>
            <h3 class="work-title">动效制作 · 内容创作</h3>
            <p class="work-desc">Wisdio宣传 · Isometry动画</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/showcase/articles" class="work-card">
            <span class="work-category">新媒体类</span>
            <h3 class="work-title">潮汕预制菜之王</h3>
            <p class="work-desc">微信公众号 · 地方产业报道</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/showcase/articles" class="work-card">
            <span class="work-category">Figma设计</span>
            <h3 class="work-title">Wisdio UI/UX</h3>
            <p class="work-desc">交互原型 · 界面设计</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="view-all">
          <a href="/showcase/articles" class="view-all-link">查看完整作品集 →</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- About -->
      <section class="section about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">关于</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
          <p>
            我正在寻找<strong>产品经理 / 用户研究</strong>相关的实习机会。
            如果你对我感兴趣，欢迎查看我的 <a href="/resume" class="link">简历</a> 或直接联系我。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <footer class="footer">
        <p>© 2024 刘扬</p>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .home {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #fafafa;
  }

  .paper {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #ffffff;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* Masthead */
  .masthead {
    padding: 80px 50px 50px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .masthead-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .masthead-title {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .masthead-subtitle {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #666;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Section */
  .section {
    padding: 40px 50px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #999;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* Intro Block */
  .intro-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    gap: 35px;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .link {
    color: #c9463d;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .link:hover {
    color: #a03a32;
  }

  .contact-info {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-divider {
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .contact-link {
    color: #666;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    color: #c9463d;
  }

  /* Projects */
  .project-item {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    padding-bottom: 30px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  }

  .project-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .project-item.featured {
    background: #fafafa;
    padding: 25px 30px;
    margin-left: -30px;
    margin-right: -30px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    border-left: 3px solid #c9463d;
  }

  .project-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .project-name {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .project-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .project-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .project-link {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #c9463d;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Works Grid */
  .works-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: #e0e0e0;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .work-card {
    padding: 25px;
    background: #fff;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .work-card:hover {
    background: #fafafa;
  }

  .work-category {
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: block;
  }

  .work-title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .work-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .view-all {
    margin-top: 25px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .view-all-link {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .view-all-link:hover {
    color: #c9463d;
  }

  /* About */
  .about-section {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    padding: 30px 50px;
    text-align: center;
    background: #fafafa;
  }

  .footer p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .masthead {
      padding: 70px 25px 40px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 30px 25px;
    }

    .intro-block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
    }

    .works-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .project-item.featured {
      margin-left: -25px;
      margin-right: -25px;
      padding: 20px 25px;
    }

    .masthead-title {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
